title: Vikings-Bears Recap, I'M MAD & TNF  Week 11 Preview
itunes:title: Vikings-Bears Recap, I'M MAD & TNF  Week 11 Preview
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Marc Sessler and Patrick Claybon start by breaking out their fears about the upcoming weakest link episode and recapping the Vikings win in primetime over the bears (6:46) . Gregg wrote a woozy banger and the heroes talk about teams that should be mad before previewing the Cardinals-Seahawks TNF game (39:39).
